---

<section id="projects">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="fade-up">
      <div class="section-tag">Selected work</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Features I've shipped.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="projects-grid">

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t1">🔐</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">Auth · Security</div>
          <div class="project-name">TOTP Multi-Factor Auth</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Designed and implemented a time-based one-time password (TOTP)
            solution using Spring Security, significantly improving account
            security for a production platform used across Austria.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">Spring Boot</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Spring Security</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Java</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">TOTP</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t2">🔗</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">Auth · Enterprise</div>
          <div class="project-name">SAML SSO Integration</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Implemented SAML-based single sign-on in collaboration with an
            external partner, enabling secure, seamless access to the online
            catalog system for their customers.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">SAML</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Spring Boot</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Java</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t3">📚</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">Full Stack · Integration</div>
          <div class="project-name">Library Ordering Module</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Built a module to integrate curated purchase proposals into a
            library ordering system — Excel import, offer management, and
            vendor API integration end-to-end.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">Java</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Spring Boot</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">PostgreSQL</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">REST API</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t4">📡</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">Hardware · Integration</div>
          <div class="project-name">RFID System Migration</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Migrated the RFID communication layer to FEIG SDK Gen 3, improving
            device communication reliability and system stability for library
            hardware.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">Java</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">FEIG SDK</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Linux</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t5">🔍</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">Search · Feature</div>
          <div class="project-name">Solr Autocomplete Search</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Implemented dynamic search with autocomplete using Apache Solr,
            paired with a reusable Drupal dropdown module for structured
            filtering — improving discoverability across the platform.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">Solr</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">PHP</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Drupal</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">JavaScript</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="project-card fade-up">
        <div class="project-thumb t6">✉</div>
        <div class="project-body">
          <div class="project-kicker">API · Integration</div>
          <div class="project-name">Transactional Email API</div>
          <div class="project-desc">
            Built a REST API integration for transactional email delivery via
            Scaleway, replacing the legacy email system with a reliable,
            scalable, and well-documented solution.
          </div>
          <div class="project-stack">
            <span class="stack-pill">Java</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Spring Boot</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">REST API</span>
            <span class="stack-pill">Scaleway</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
